This lightweight package is based on the Apache-2.0 licensed implementation of
"Adversarial Defect Synthesis for Industrial Products in Low Data Regime" by
Pasquale Coscia, Angelo Genovese, Fabio Scotti, and Vincenzo Piuri.

The demo dataset included in data/demo_dataset and data/demo_input is synthetic
and generated by scripts/make_demo_dataset.py.
